{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e49f474fd2","title":"对日本首相岸信介关于中国经济现状和前途的评论的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c9c813f602","index":0,"year":1959,"month":7,"day":27,"articleId":"e49f474fd2"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"6b48eed2b4","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是对中国驻德意志民主共和国大使馆1959年7月20日关于岸信介访问德意志联邦共和国给外交部的报告的批语。"},{"id":"b1f002bd99","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"岸信介的这段话是他在波恩举行的记者招待会上谈到中日关系时说的。中国驻德意志民主共和国大便馆在报告中转引了这段话。"}],"contents":[{"id":"468d2b54ab","type":"title","text":"对日本首相岸信介关于中国经济现状和前途的评论的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2"},{"id":"6b48eed2b4","type":"paragraph","text":"印发各同志。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2"},{"id":"b1f002bd99","type":"paragraph","text":"我想请同志们看一下岸信介的话。他说：“在完成长期计划当中，中国像其他共产主义国家一样，固然也存在看困难，但是鉴子","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2"},{"id":"b2e4a71141","type":"subtitle","text":"目前的成就，人们必须说：中国的远景并不是不顺利的。”怎么","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2"},{"id":"f57394e2e9","type":"paragraph","text":"样？这个日本大资产阶级的代表人物对于我国经济现状和前途的评论，不是说得相当正确吗？他比我们的一些悲观主义者，泄气主义者，就对同一事件的评论这一点来说，不是还要好一些吗","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2"},{"id":"71284d3ba6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2"},{"id":"c705b80054","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十七日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2"}],"page":{"id":"dad5bf0d2e","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"e49f474fd2","start":230,"end":230}}}},"__N_SSG":true}